\n<Manu><WordWrap>Excuse me but do you know where the caretaker of Sta. Monica Church is?
\n<CareTaker><WordWrap>I am the caretaker. What do you want?
\n<Manu><WordWrap>Ok listen sir. I need your help I was able to find the missing contestants inside a cave and the bridge collapsed and I need your tools and equipment to build another bridge.
\n<CareTaker><WordWrap>You want to build a bridge? Fine you can use my tools.
\n<CareTaker><WordWrap>The tools you need are an Axe and a Hammer. Do you have any of those?
\n<Manu><WordWrap>I already got an Axe. I only need the Hammer.
\n<CareTaker><WordWrap>Ok there should be a Hammer inside a chest in my house.
\n<CareTaker><WordWrap>Its a house with a red roof. Look inside the house and find the Hammer inside the chest.
\n<CareTaker><WordWrap>You might need some rope and nails to make the bridge. Don't worry the chest with the hammer has some nails and rope to help you build the bridge.
\n<CareTaker><WordWrap>If your short on supply or materials, there's a shop nearby in the right to buy the thing you need.
Look inside the buildings/houses to find the tools to build the bridge
\n<CareTaker><WordWrap>I could lend you my Axe for a while.
